      <title>欧洲准备将巴塞尔银行交易规则推迟一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/europe-poised-to-delay-basel-bank-trading-rules-by-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，欧盟将把全球银行资本规则的关键部分推迟一年实施，以便欧盟银行机构不会因美国标准持续争论而处于不利地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/europe-poised-to-delay-basel-bank-trading-rules-by-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 13:19:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前 NatWest 首席执行官 Alison Rose 加入私募股权公司 Charterhouse 担任顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/ex-natwest-ceo-alison-rose-joins-pe-firm-charterhouse-as-adviser</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前 NatWest Group Plc 老板 Alison Rose 已加入私募股权公司 Charterhouse Capital Partners 担任高级顾问，这是她在离开这家英国银行一年后重返伦敦金融城。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/ex-natwest-ceo-alison-rose-joins-pe-firm-charterhouse-as-adviser</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 13:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国电网不会向家庭支付明年冬季电力需求抑制费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/uk-grid-won-t-pay-homes-to-curb-power-demand-next-winter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计英国发电缓冲将有所改善，英国电网将排除明年冬季向客户付费以减少用电的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/uk-grid-won-t-pay-homes-to-curb-power-demand-next-winter</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 13:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油钻探公司 Vista Energy 将根据 SLB 协议进口新的压裂设备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/oil-driller-vista-energy-to-import-new-frack-set-in-slb-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷石油钻探公司 Vista Energy 与 SLB 签署了一项协议，将于今年下半年进口新的水力压裂阵列，以帮助提高 Vaca Muerta 页岩地区的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/oil-driller-vista-energy-to-import-new-frack-set-in-slb-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 13:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚在首个违约后计划中将预算提高至 170 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/ethiopia-hikes-budget-to-17-billion-in-first-post-default-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚将在 2025 年预算中增加 21% 的支出，这是其自拖欠欧洲债券偿还债务并承诺与国际货币基金组织就经济改革进行谈判以来的首次增加支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/ethiopia-hikes-budget-to-17-billion-in-first-post-default-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 12:50:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西通胀加速，再次降息希望渺茫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/brazil-inflation-speeds-up-and-hurts-hopes-of-another-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西5月份的年度通胀率升幅超过预期，结束了连续七个月的物价下降趋势，并给政策制定者在下周的会议上维持利率不变带来更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/brazil-inflation-speeds-up-and-hurts-hopes-of-another-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 12:08:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国债券市场下跌，马克龙拒绝辞职传闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/macron-says-election-result-doesn-t-affect-president-s-position</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，他作为法国总统的地位不会受到立法选举结果的影响，因为他考虑辞职的一份报告引发了法国政府债券的大幅抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/macron-says-election-result-doesn-t-affect-president-s-position</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 11:58:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织在最新评估中削减肯尼亚融资计划规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/imf-and-kenya-reach-initial-agreement-to-access-1-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于肯尼亚的融资条件更加宽松，国际货币基金组织已缩减了对肯尼亚的项目规模，同时朝着解锁剩余资金的方向迈出了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/imf-and-kenya-reach-initial-agreement-to-access-1-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:09:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对美国收益率的敏感性增强，比特币面临“关键”的 36 小时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/bitcoin-btc-faces-risky-36-hours-on-sensitivity-to-us-yields-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储利率决议和美国关键通胀数据公布前，全球市场紧张不安。比特币投资者有理由对潜在波动保持特别警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/bitcoin-btc-faces-risky-36-hours-on-sensitivity-to-us-yields-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 06:19:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国市场前景和周三美联储决议公布前油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在市场前景报告公布以及石油输出国组织维持需求增强的预测之际，油价录得自 3 月份以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-11</guid>
